  "title": "Pet Grooming Assistants / Apprentices (Full Time - Tampines |$1500 - $2500)",
  "description": "<p>The Pets Workshop is looking to expand the team and we are looking for full time pet grooming assistants / apprentices to join us!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our pet grooming assistants are critical members of our team. They assist our pet stylists with basic pet grooming care, starting with showering of pets, blow drying them, brushing them, clipping of their nails, cleaning of their ears. On top of that, they assist to maintain the cleanliness of our salon and attending to customers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We welcome applicants who are patient, would like to learn more about the industry, and have a lot of love for animals. Prior experience is great, but if you do not have that, it is okay too! We would be happy to coach you along the way and impart our knowledge and skills to you. You would also be someone who is a team-player and would be able to commit long term. Strong communication skill and being familiar with social media will help too!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We also offer apprenticeship for interested talents who would like to pick up professional pet grooming skills!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We provide:</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Very competitive and flexible pay scheme + performance bonus + allowance</p>\n<p>2. A great learning environment and opportunity for you to learn about the pet industry</p>\n<p>3. Friendly co-workers and mentors</p>\n<p>4. Medical insurance coverage</p>\n<p>5. Company-sponsored gatherings</p>\n<p>6. And of course many fluffy furkids for you to work with!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Reach out now to know more!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
